msgctxt "116_Man"
msgid "You know, I'm pretty freakin' strong. I've done karate, boxing, and muay thai. You don't like getting hurt, do you?"
msgstr "Sabes, soy jodidamente fuerte. He hecho kárate, boxeo y muay thai. No te gusta que te hagan daño, verdad?"

msgctxt "128_Man"
msgid "Just leave your wallet and get outta here."
msgstr "Solo deja tu cartera y vete."

msgctxt "152_Man"
msgid "My bad... To be honest, I've never done any martial arts."
msgstr "Culpa mía... Sinceramente nunca he hecho artes marciales."

msgctxt "164_Man"
msgid "Here, please have mercy."
msgstr "Por favor, ten piedad."

msgctxt "176_Man"
msgid "You got a lovely %s."
msgstr "Obtuviste un %s."

msgctxt "212_Man"
msgid "I mean... I did watch a ton of DVDs..."
msgstr "Quiero decir... He visto montañas de DVDs..."

